# thoth_fleet_api_key

Issues short-lived fleet-scoped API keys.

Organization-scoped keys are intentionally not creatable through Terraform/Pulumi.
Create organization keys with `thothctl api-keys create ...` and pass them to
the provider via `THOTH_API_KEY` or `org_api_key`.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "thoth_fleet_api_key" "fleet_ops" {
  name            = "fleet-ops"
  scope_target_id = "fleet-001"
  permissions     = ["read", "write"]
  ttl_seconds     = 3600
  jit_reason      = "fleet-maintenance-window"
}
```
